br />\n<br />\n原圖：無綫新聞截圖、陳雲Facebook專頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75?hc_ref=PAGES_TIMELINE&amp;fref=nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%3Fhc_ref%3DPAGES_TIMELINE%26fref%3Dnf&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTS3aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=6faaa193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75?hc_ref=PAGES_TIMELINE&amp;fref=nf</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"講獨派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1f0c769be2c75229ba297147b4f395bf0d55b0","tid":1166000,"uid":2748,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"因人廢言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305d7b854026ac6ac64e718bd125313864965d4a","tid":1166000,"uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:25:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">請問StableCoin(會員#2748)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1118548\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1118548</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"8a88cb43d462aad1e6c46d716f9632a061b2d640","tid":1166000,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0fb3c3589e98892045e26bcc86fd835bc8ec5e","tid":1166000,"uid":76776,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:42:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b978c312b5e65d12da5f33540e8c574038323eb","tid":1166000,"uid":189,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:43:39.000Z","msg":"國師打飛機打到腎虧啦，黃台仰仲要去埋佢母校讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7639a5c59381e32bf2b7dc8a44381ddbc6f049e8","tid":1166000,"uid":